---
import { brandLogos } from "../../data/home";
---

<section class="bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,_#f8f8f8,_#f2f2f2)] px-5 py-16 sm:px-8 sm:py-20 lg:px-12 lg:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[980px] text-center">
    <span class="inline-flex rounded-full border border-neutral-200 bg-white px-6 py-3 font-['Montserrat'] text-[13px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-neutral-600 shadow-[0_8px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)]">
      Buscar por marca
    </span>
    <h2 class="mt-5 font-['Montserrat'] text-[42px] font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#111111] sm:text-[56px]">Explora marcas</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 font-['Montserrat'] text-[14px] uppercase tracking-[0.34em] text-neutral-500 sm:text-[15px]">por fabricante</p>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-7 max-w-[48ch] text-[18px] leading-9 text-neutral-600">
      Marcas con mas rotacion en portales alemanes. Este bloque funciona bien para destacar fabricantes objetivo o filtrar por grupo VAG.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-[1120px] grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-6">
    {brandLogos.map((logo, index) => (
      <div class="group flex h-[108px] items-center justify-center rounded-3xl border border-[#e8e8e8] bg-white/95 p-6 shadow-[0_12px_28px_rgba(0,0,0,0.04)] transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-red-200 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] sm:h-[116px]">
        <img
          src={logo}
          alt={`Logo de marca de coche ${index + 1} mostrado en la seccion de marcas`}
          loading="lazy"
          class="max-h-12 w-auto object-contain opacity-95 transition duration-300 group-hover:opacity-100 sm:max-h-14"
        />
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>
  <div class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-[980px] text-center">
    <p class="font-['Montserrat'] text-[13px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-neutral-500 sm:text-[14px]">
      Puedes cambiar logos, tamanos y columnas desde el array <span class="text-neutral-600">brandLogos</span> y estas clases de la misma seccion.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
